{"tid":1851630,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"啲慈善機構NGO死撚曬去邊，每次依啲時候都失蹤？","createTime":"2020-01-30T06:09:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-01T00:48:48.000Z","uid":36702,"like":56,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"5d5a84ce03f6df02709cb9f4a047bdd0d5f10f45","tid":1851630,"uid":36702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T06:09:22.000Z","msg":"大家真係狠心啲，咪撚再捐錢比香港任何一間大型NGO   <br />\n<br />\n旗都咪撚買  全部都係肥上瘦下    捐款變撚曬做行政費 手續費  變相比錢佢地大魚大肉<br />\n<br />\n根本無做過野，有大事都唔會出黎幫手<br />\n<br />\n咁撚多老人家唔識買口罩 買消毒用品    竟然唔出黎幫 ？<br />\n<br />\n啲慈善機構平時送米送乜  關鍵時候就攜同大家嘅捐款縮返入老母塊閪度<br />\n<br />\n仲有某幾間係公務員都被要求HOME OFFICE嘅情況下 <br />\n<br />\n仍然要求全體員工緊守崗位   冒住中武漢肺炎嘅風險去返工 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"962269c119877b6311b2d5ea3df8408b3dc4fe17","tid":1851630,"uid":36702,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T06:12:13.000Z","msg":"保X局  係咪死撚曬啲人？<br />\n<br />\n拍個垃圾show籌旗都唔幫下啲基層長者買口罩買消毒用品？？"},{"pid":"10dc4cea1b4fc909dfe2d7c57b8177871be70ddd","tid":1851630,"uid":36702,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T06:14:24.000Z","msg":"仲要講埋  <br />\n<br />\n十間有十間都奶共奶人民幣  親政府R funding <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n每次都政府/建制吹雞  即刻跪低"},{"pid":"fa26be80269ea202c17ce199d7fe20715016d608","tid":1851630,"uid":36702,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T06:16:57.000Z","msg":"正垃圾  大家真係狠心咪撚再幫啲大機構買旗/捐錢   <br />\n<br />\n全部都係呃鳩人<br />\n<br />\n街上有啲垃圾「sales」搵你捐錢<br />\n<br />\n問下條友捐撚左上個月啲佣金未先  <br />\n<br />\n留返啲錢去星火 立場  好過 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d052a24353f682403de8b498c26c4414c453ba9","tid":1851630,"uid":124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T06:17:10.000Z","msg":"一筆過撥款之下邊有咁多額外資源<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲要依家周圍都缺貨 訂都要時間<br />\n<br />\n班老人家不知幾醒<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6c477e776e07340ac34d9c8fce5da1afc98c432","tid":1851630,"uid":36702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T06:21:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b91e99e8ed97b53ade7b4bce767b876913a346d","tid":1851630,"uid":24443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T06:23:41.000Z","msg":"而家先知<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0873f3877e9943591b7cd1cf120fedd59d853dec","tid":1851630,"uid":55309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T06:28:08.000Z","msg":"從來一蚊都唔撚會捐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2da3f69272d525ac5bc55ac5f34d9c10453ad25","tid":1851630,"uid":201604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T06:28:50.000Z","msg":"冇得呃捐款 出黎托柒咩"},{"pid":"1eed534f7fd99245a4f736264037371e9c006f39","tid":1851630,"uid":112241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T06:29:29.000Z","msg":"你真係信有呢的機構？拿錢時先有的所謂高層出現<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e36bcf75017d3c440bacd1e669797821ae02ff6","tid":1851630,"uid":36702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0873f3877e9943591b7cd1cf120fedd59d853dec","tid":1851630,"uid":55309,"like":0,"dislike":0,